text: Albin Kurti (born 24 March 1975) is a Kosovar Albanian politician and activist. He is the prime minister of Kosovo since 22 March 2021. He was prime minister before from February and June 2020. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Prime Ministers of Kosovo Category:Current national leaders Category:People from Pristina
